    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Due to a fact-checking error, in some editions of Wednesday's Times, Maureen Dowd's column cited the wrong former Iraqi official as critical of the U.S. invasion of Iraq. He was Ali Allawi, the former finance minister, not Ayad Allawi, the former prime minister.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Due to a fact-checking error, in some editions of Wednesday's Times, Maureen Dowd's column cited the wrong former Iraqi official as critical of the U.S. invasion of Iraq. He was Ali Allawi, the former finance minister, not Ayad Allawi, the former prime minister.</p>
      </block>
